                    </a>

                    <!-- Intro -->
                    <p class="text-secondary mt-3" dmx-html="meta">
                        Of all things which wisdom provides to make life entirely happy, much the greatest is the possession of friendship. It is not so much our friends' help that helps us, as the confidence of their help.
                    </p>

                    <!-- Read more -->
                    <a href="#!" class="d-inline-block border-bottom border-primary text-decoration-none mt-2 pb-1" dmx-bind:href="'blog/'+path">Leer Artículo</a>
                </div>

                <!-- Side posts -->
                <div class="col-lg-5 pt-5 pt-lg-0 pl-lg-4" id="">

                    <!-- Post -->
                    <div class="row mb-0 pb-4" id="repeatright" dmx-repeat:repeatright="data_view2.data">
                        <div class="col-md-6">
                            <!-- Featured image -->
                            <a href="#!" dmx-bind:href="'blog/'+path">
                                <img class="img-fluid rounded hover-lift-light" alt="" dmx-bind:src="img" loading="lazy">
                            </a>
                        </div>
                        <div class="col-md-6 pt-3">
                            <!-- Title -->
                            <a href="#!" class="h5 d-block text-dark text-decoration-none" dmx-html="title" dmx-bind:href="'blog/'+path">
                                The happiness of your life depends upon the quality of your thoughts
                            </a>

                            <!-- Read more -->
                            <a href="#!" class="d-inline-block border-bottom border-primary text-decoration-none mt-2 pb-1" dmx-bind:href="'blog/'+path" dmx-on:click="">Leer Artículo</a>
                        </div>
                    </div>

